parameters: \n<Robert Edward Jr.>I'm right at home on this throne!
\n<Robert Edward Jr.>Oh, it's just a chair?
\n<Robert Edward Jr.>This castle is very large. I'm amazed that
it hasn't collapsed over the past millenium.
\n<Robert Edward Jr.>I suppose the Last Stand must have cast some
sort of enchantment along with the seal in order
to keep the castle's structural integrity.
\n<Roberta Edward>You were... brave. When you opened the seal.
\p3Is that... what's a red slime doing here?
\p2It sees us! Let's take it out!
\earlMy name... is Earl. I'm a traveling slime,
and honestly, I'm not sure how I got here.
\earlI closed my eyes for a minute, and when I woke
up, everyone I knew from the castle was gone, and
the place was overrun with monsters. Oddly enough,
there's also a lot less light coming in from outside.
\earlI'm just trying to stay alive. I've been
living off scavenged materials, but the
monsters here don't see me as a friend,
so I have to be careful while looting.
\earlSay, maybe we could strike a deal? I could
sell you some of my items here! For a fair
price, of course. And you four can clear up
the place so I can scavenge for more items!
you're lucky we didn't kill you.
\earlI know, I know... come here now and then
to see what new things I've got in stock.
Oh, and you can use these beds to rest
if you get hurt. That's free of charge!
\earlHello hello! Would you like to see
what supplies I have in stock?
Would you like to rest here?
